# GitHub Actions Secrets — Hostinger (document root TIDAK bisa diubah)
#
# Workflow build frontend lalu upload ke FTP. Jika FTP_DIST_DIR staging
# (/public_html/frontend/dist/), workflow otomatis publish juga ke /public_html/.
#
#   VITE_API_URL   = https://portal.universitaspgridelta.ac.id/api
#   FTP_HOST       = 46.202.138.30          (IP hPanel, JANGAN pakai domain/Cloudflare)
#   FTP_USERNAME   = u278744870.portal.universitaspgridelta.ac.id
#   FTP_PASSWORD   = password FTP hPanel (hindari karakter khusus di secret)
#   FTP_DIST_DIR   = /public_html/          (langsung ke document root)
#                    atau /public_html/frontend/dist/ (workflow auto-publish ke root)
#
# Jika FTP timeout dari GitHub Actions: Hostinger kadang blokir IP GHA.
# Workflow mencoba lftp (4x retry) → FTPS fallback → plain FTP fallback.
#
# Backend .env di server (tambahkan):
#   APP_URL=https://portal.universitaspgridelta.ac.id
#   FRONTEND_URL=https://portal.universitaspgridelta.ac.id
